.TH "snd_hdac_bus_add_device" 9 "snd_hdac_bus_add_device" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
snd_hdac_bus_add_device \- Add a codec to bus
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" snd_hdac_bus_add_device
.BI "(struct hdac_bus *bus "  ","
.BI "struct hdac_device *codec "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bus" 12
HDA core bus
.IP "codec" 12
HDA core device to add
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Adds the given codec to the list in the bus.  The caddr_tbl array
and codec_powered bits are updated, as well.
Returns zero if success, or a negative error code.
